Egypt has been a republic since 18 June 1953. President [[Hosni Mubarak|Mohamed Hosni Mubarak]] has been the [[President of Egypt|President of the Republic]] since 14 October 1981, after the assassination of President [[Anwar Sadat|Mohammed Anwar El-Sadat]]. Mubarak is currently serving his fifth term in office (28 years). He is the leader of the ruling [[National Democratic Party (Egypt)|National Democratic Party]].
